    <item>
      <title>Hulu Channel Drop Down Menu</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/interface/hulu-channel-drop-down-menu/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Oct 2008 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/interface/hulu-channel-drop-down-menu/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hulu&#39;s drop down menu for channels stretches to the width of the design and provides a multi-column grid of channels. This method of running a drop down or flyout menu left-to-right rather than top-to-bottom allows interface designers to present longer lists of options without worrying about what appears in relation to the fold, and forcing scroll on longer lists.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div id=&#34;screens-full&#34; class=&#34;clear&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;fullimg clear&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/interface/hulu-channel-drop-menu-1.png&#34; class=&#34;group&#34; rel=&#34;group&#34; title=&#34;1. &#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/interface/hulu-channel-drop-menu-1.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;img-responsive&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;        
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.hulu.com/&#34;&gt;http://www.hulu.com/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
