&lt;div id=&#34;screens-full&#34; class=&#34;clear&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;1. Home page.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;fullimg clear&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/interface/ikea-nav-1.png&#34; class=&#34;group&#34; rel=&#34;group&#34; title=&#34;1. Home page.&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/interface/ikea-nav-1.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;img-responsive&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;screens-full&#34; class=&#34;clear&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;2. &amp;quot;Living Room&amp;quot; selected in the global navigation. Local navigation appears in the left sidebar.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;fullimg clear&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/interface/ikea-nav-2.png&#34; class=&#34;group&#34; rel=&#34;group&#34; title=&#34;2. &amp;quot;Living Room&amp;quot; selected in the global navigation. Local navigation appears in the left s...&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/interface/ikea-nav-2.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;img-responsive&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;screens-full&#34; class=&#34;clear&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;3. Selecting a local nav link in the left sidebar expand that branch of the local tree.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;fullimg clear&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/interface/ikea-nav-3.png&#34; class=&#34;group&#34; rel=&#34;group&#34; title=&#34;3. Selecting a local nav link in the left sidebar expand that branch of the local tree.&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/interface/ikea-nav-3.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;img-responsive&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;screens-full&#34; class=&#34;clear&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;4. Selected links in the tree are highlighted.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;fullimg clear&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/interface/ikea-nav-4.png&#34; class=&#34;group&#34; rel=&#34;group&#34; title=&#34;4. Selected links in the tree are highlighted.&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/interface/ikea-nav-4.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;img-responsive&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;screens-full&#34; class=&#34;clear&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;5. The &amp;quot;All Departments&amp;quot; link in the global navigation displays the expanded top level of the tree.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;fullimg clear&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/interface/ikea-nav-5.png&#34; class=&#34;group&#34; rel=&#34;group&#34; title=&#34;5. The &amp;quot;All Departments&amp;quot; link in the global navigation displays the expanded top level of ...&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/interface/ikea-nav-5.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;img-responsive&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;screens-full&#34; class=&#34;clear&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;6. Selecting a branch in &amp;quot;All Departments&amp;quot; doesn&#39;t display a selected link in the global nav.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;fullimg clear&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/interface/ikea-nav-6.png&#34; class=&#34;group&#34; rel=&#34;group&#34; title=&#34;6. Selecting a branch in &amp;quot;All Departments&amp;quot; doesn&#39;t display a selected link in the glo...&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/interface/ikea-nav-6.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;img-responsive&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;        
